trans-unit.source: Represents the Dispatcher when it is in a disable state and provides a means to re-enable dispatcher processing.
trans-unit.target: Representa o Dispatcher quando ele está em um estado desabilitado e fornece um meio de habilitar o processamento do dispatcher novamente.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A> returns a <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled> object when it is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A> Retorna um <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled> quando ele é chamado de objeto.

trans-unit.source: Disabling dispatcher processing is an advanced method that is intended to eliminate the chance of unrelated reentrancy.
trans-unit.target: Desabilitar o processamento do dispatcher é um método avançado que é destinado para eliminar a chance de reentrância não relacionada.

trans-unit.source: The effects of disabling processing are as follows:
trans-unit.target: Os efeitos de desabilitar o processamento são da seguinte maneira:

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr#initcap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-clrsharpinitcap-md.md)] locks will not pump messages internally.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr#initcap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-clrsharpinitcap-md.md)] os bloqueios serão não bomba de mensagens internamente.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherFrame> objects are not allowed to be pushed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherFrame> objetos não podem ser enviados por push.

trans-unit.source: Message processing is not permitted.
trans-unit.target: Processamento de mensagem não é permitido.

trans-unit.source: Calling <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled.Dispose%2A> on the <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled> object will re-enable dispatcher processing.
trans-unit.target: Chamando <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled.Dispose%2A> no <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled> objeto reativará o processamento do dispatcher.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to disable dispatcher processing and re-enable dispatcher processing.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como o processamento do dispatcher de desabilitar e reabilitar o processamento do dispatcher.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A> is called in a **using** statement.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A> é chamado em um **usando** instrução.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A> returns a <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled> structure which is used as the object to be disposed when the **using** block finishes.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A> Retorna um <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled> estrutura que é usada como o objeto a ser descartado quando o **usando** bloquear for concluída.

trans-unit.source: Calling <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled.Dispose%2A> on the <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled> structure re-enables dispatcher processing.
trans-unit.target: Chamando <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled.Dispose%2A> no <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled> estrutura habilita novamente o processamento do dispatcher.

trans-unit.source: Re-enables dispatcher processing.
trans-unit.target: Habilita o processamento do dispatcher novamente.

trans-unit.source: Disabling dispatcher processing is an advanced method that is intended to eliminate the chance of unrelated reentrancy.
trans-unit.target: Desabilitar o processamento do dispatcher é um método avançado que é destinado para eliminar a chance de reentrância não relacionada.

trans-unit.source: The effects of disabling processing are as follows:

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr#initcap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-clrsharpinitcap-md.md)] locks will not pump messages internally.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr#initcap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-clrsharpinitcap-md.md)] os bloqueios serão não bomba de mensagens internamente.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherFrame> objects are not allowed to be pushed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherFrame> objetos não podem ser enviados por push.

trans-unit.source: Message processing is not permitted.
trans-unit.target: Processamento de mensagem não é permitido.
